# Dogfooding — agentboard runs against its own repo to generate real usage
# data. The .platform/ pack tracks our live work (streams, checkpoints,
# memory) but is local-only; only the kit itself is versioned.
.platform/
.codex/
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.json.agentboard-backup-*




